115
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:52,660
Why did Douzi take you here?

116
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:54,740
Did she already know

117
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:56,100
that you were the Princess of Shengdong?

118
00:05:58,380 --> 00:05:59,580
