156
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,420
Why do you break

157
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,220
into the Tianji Mansion?

158
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,500
Please forgive me.

159
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:31,780
